Chile  hired  Blackrock Inc. (BLK) , Rogge
Global Partners Plc and Mellon Capital Management Corp. to
manage a portion of the countryâ€™s $4.5 billion of pension
savings held abroad.  Blackrock Institutional Trust Company NA and Rogge will
manage the corporate fixed-income portfolio and Blackrock and
